13. What can you do to save a programme from crashing if it encounters an error? 

solution :

I use try and execpt clause for that code to save my programme from crashing if that code encounters an error
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
14. What is the purpose of the try clause? What is the purpose of the except clause? 

solution :
the purpose of try clause is to protect the code from crashing and moves to except clause if error happens
the purpose of except clause is to handle is the code that is crashed in try clause.
